{"tid":854491,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓市大減價】太古城劈近200萬易手 代理：市場無客","createTime":"2018-10-09T11:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T05:00:20.000Z","uid":174649,"like":80,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"a7574955664e15139fddb2b377bb767dce1d84a5","tid":854491,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181009/large/1539063214_5abc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F1539063214_5abc.jpg&h=fc7c9d22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓市全方位劈價，一直被視作樓市寒暑表的鰂魚涌太古城，剛錄得本月第二宗成交，業主減價近200萬元沽貨。<br />\n<br />\n即日其他減價成交新聞：<br />\n【滙景相連戶賣平兩球】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2OOw8Ik\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OOw8Ik&d=MUqSzCzHwhhixO6PguiJ4Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c997e6f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2OOw8Ik</a> <br />\n【長實名門蝕兩球沽】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2yyjMKv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yyjMKv&d=MUqSzCzHwhhixO6PguiJ4Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=abdd28b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2yyjMKv</a> <br />\n【碧海藍天兩房劈110萬沽】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Pn6vLT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Pn6vLT&d=MUqSzCzHwhhixO6PguiJ4Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ee557f16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Pn6vLT</a><br />\n<br />\n中原地產張光耀表示，翠榕閣高層E室，實用面積922方呎，望園景，原叫價1,950萬元，放盤逾半年仍賣不到心目中價位，直至近日市況轉差，業主見難得有客還價，大幅減價192萬以1,758萬元沽貨，減幅9.9%，呎價19,067元。對上同類成交為紫樺閣中層E室，同面積，今年6月造價1,898萬元，是次賣平140萬元。<br />\n<br />\n此單位獲中銀及滙豐網上估值2,001萬及2,174萬元，造價較估值低最多416萬元或19%。<br />\n張光耀續稱，現時太古城約三成業主肯減價，但問題是市場無客，睇樓客也不多，業主肯減價也沒用，所以屋苑自8月份後交投非常淡靜，上月全月僅兩宗成交，料創屋苑歷史低位。"},{"pid":"c5c1f49d0959196220a53442bf0a47daef51949e","tid":854491,"uid":51787,"like":323,"dislike":7,"score":316,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:41:51.000Z","msg":"諗唔到原因唔計，總知唔計"},{"pid":"74454fb7e794fa9cfe9fa06dd260919dd757ec89","tid":854491,"uid":162478,"like":74,"dislike":2,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:43:03.000Z","msg":"太古城好難唔計wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca98ff602bae0d0e9ec392d51ab7b11a12dc9446","tid":854491,"uid":175523,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:44:41.000Z","msg":"唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16f010d96ac981956765ae8bf827705796c02ff","tid":854491,"uid":27319,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:46:01.000Z","msg":"個別例子 唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f1bc34c026ded245b3789f0103f9a2d5061922","tid":854491,"uid":23190,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:55:39.000Z","msg":"太古城唔計"},{"pid":"9159c28b5ea5eab1a6190f8aedcb16e3a3c27aae","tid":854491,"uid":10101,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:56:29.000Z","msg":"2萬5一個月，200萬可以租6.6年<br />\n<br />\n不過，<br />\n自住驚閪咩"},{"pid":"146f5830818afed2556698a71206bcb411ad20b6","tid":854491,"uid":61529,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:56:39.000Z","msg":"減價200萬都1700萬啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d38dbd7c172db77d30091251f4bb328c00c280","tid":854491,"uid":158889,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:57:41.000Z","msg":"好難計 wo 唔計"},{"pid":"9dfcb374fe7c1689de31978837c129edb9a4469d","tid":854491,"uid":172890,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"減價三成唔信冇客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40287c9a0493a3fc8d1af58153a98695e6456285","tid":854491,"uid":33443,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:01:49.000Z","msg":"千七萬唔計啦"},{"pid":"bef53e4b8f4eee033edc157387446f9698069bf1","tid":854491,"uid":94454,