jMKv&d=MUqSzCzHwhhixO6PguiJ4Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=abdd28b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2yyjMKv</a> <br />\n【碧海藍天兩房劈110萬沽】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Pn6vLT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Pn6vLT&d=MUqSzCzHwhhixO6PguiJ4Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ee557f16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Pn6vLT</a><br />\n<br />\n中原地產張光耀表示，翠榕閣高層E室，實用面積922方呎，望園景，原叫價1,950萬元，放盤逾半年仍賣不到心目中價位，直至近日市況轉差，業主見難得有客還價，大幅減價192萬以1,758萬元沽貨，減幅9.9%，呎價19,067元。對上同類成交為紫樺閣中層E室，同面積，今年6月造價1,898萬元，是次賣平140萬元。<br />\n<br />\n此單位獲中銀及滙豐網上估值2,001萬及2,174萬元，造價較估值低最多416萬元或19%。<br />\n張光耀續稱，現時太古城約三成業主肯減價，但問題是市場無客，睇樓客也不多，業主肯減價也沒用，所以屋苑自8月份後交投非常淡靜，上月全月僅兩宗成交，料創屋苑歷史低位。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T13:23:00.000Z","msg":"我反而好奇銀行個估價仲咁硬嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n銀行唔肯面對現實？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e1fc22f7d5a1c92cdeaf79311953d1ff96f1e0","tid":854491,"uid":171446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a12b954e72d7f642d2298f10b76677352c05cf2","tid":854491,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37e1fc22f7d5a1c92cdeaf79311953d1ff96f1e0","tid":854491,"uid":171446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e5715058115a6d5dde7860f2bfa927d08237698","tid":854491,"uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a7574955664e15139fddb2b377bb767dce1d84a5","tid":854491,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181009/large/1539063214_5abc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181009%2Flarge