貴 點計阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd7baa4bf78ec95203fda29dd0cb87aaec7ad49","tid":854491,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa9f7bad77661d7119833c8a7431363b6dfea05c","tid":854491,"uid":47776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5a3718f2b3bbbffd27670a7503a688d5ed41781","tid":854491,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181009/large/1539063214_5abc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F1539063214_5abc.jpg&h=fc7c9d22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓市全方位劈價，一直被視作樓市寒暑表的鰂魚涌太古城，剛錄得本月第二宗成交，業主減價近200萬元沽貨。<br />\n<br />\n即日其他減價成交新聞：<br />\n【滙景相連戶賣平兩球】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2OOw8Ik\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OOw8Ik&d=MUqSzCzHwhhixO6PguiJ4Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c997e6f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2OOw8Ik</a> <br />\n【長實名門蝕兩球沽】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2yyjMKv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yyjMKv&d=MUqSzCzHwhhixO6PguiJ4Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=abdd28b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2yyjMKv</a> <br />\n【碧海藍天兩房劈110萬沽】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Pn6vLT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Pn6vLT&d=MUqSzCzHwhhixO6PguiJ4Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ee557f16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Pn6vLT</a><br />\n<br />\n中原地產張光耀表示，翠榕閣高層E室，實用面積922方呎，望園景，原叫價1,950萬元，放盤逾半年仍賣不到心目中價位，直至近日市況轉差，業主見難得有客還價，大幅減價192萬以1,758萬元沽貨，減幅9.9%，呎價19,067元。對上同類成交為紫樺閣中層E室，同面積，今年6月造價1,898萬元，是次賣平140萬元。<br />\n<br />\n此單位獲中銀及滙豐網上估值2,001萬及2,174萬元，造價較估值低最多416萬元或19%。<br />\n張光耀續稱，現時太古城約三成業主肯減價，但問題是市場無客，睇樓客也不多，業主肯減價也沒用，所以屋苑自8月份後交投非常淡靜，上月全月僅兩宗成交，料創屋苑歷史低位。</blockquote>我反而好奇銀行個估價仲咁硬嘅<br />\n<br />\n銀行唔肯面對現實？</blockquote>成交左今次會唔會拖低估值？</blockquote><br />\n點可能唔會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T13:58:28.000Z","msg":"聽講剛需可以頂返上去不是嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:43:13.000Z","msg":"冇咩係是剛需解釋唔到<br />\n如果有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86652c9504318a0e65671438f7978ec3eb4c0fd","tid":854491,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dfcb374fe7c1689de31978837c129edb9a4469d","tid":854491,"uid":172890,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"減價三成唔信冇客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:49:16.000Z","msg":"短炒都抵"}]}